Package nl.b3p.csw.jaxb.csw

Class CapabilitiesType

  • java.lang.Object
    • nl.b3p.csw.jaxb.ows.CapabilitiesBaseType
      • nl.b3p.csw.jaxb.csw.CapabilitiesType
  • public class CapabilitiesType
extends CapabilitiesBaseType
    This type extends ows:CapabilitiesBaseType defined in OGC-05-008 to include information about supported OGC filter components. A profile may extend this type to describe additional capabilities.

    Java class for CapabilitiesType complex type.

    The following schema fragment specifies the expected content contained within this class. 

     <complexType name="CapabilitiesType">
   <complexContent>
     <extension base="{http://www.opengis.net/ows}CapabilitiesBaseType">
       <sequence>
         <element ref="{http://www.opengis.net/ogc}Filter_Capabilities"/>
       </sequence>
     </extension>
   </complexContent>
 </complexType>
